headline: Waymo may be worth $200B+ using Tesla as benchmark—DA Davidson
summary: Investing.com -- DA Davidson said in a note to clients on Tuesday that Alphabet’s (NASDAQ:GOOGL) Waymo unit could be worth more than $200 billion as a standalone company, citing comparisons with Tesla’s robotaxi ambitions and urging a breakup of Alphabet to unlock shareholder value.
